FairTrack is source-available. Private, non-commercial use, modification and
contributions are permitted. Distributing the software or derivative works —
including app-store publishing — is only permitted with clear attribution to
the original project ("Based on FairTrack,
https://github.com/daonware-it/FairTrack"), with this license included and
changes marked. Distributing copies without attribution (re-skins) is
prohibited. Commercial distribution requires prior written consent. Provided
"as is", without warranty.
